{"tid":1854024,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"＜學術討論＞重用口罩，密實袋中高溫消毒法","createTime":"2020-01-31T09:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T17:41:23.000Z","uid":232065,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3a868f3fa31bbfbd7769f3bc8752ff97aafeacee","tid":1854024,"uid":232065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:42:01.000Z","msg":"***僅學術討論***<br />\n**你家有大量口罩，不等於所有人都能買到口罩**<br />\n<br />\n根據SARS研究報告，<br />\nSARS病毒可被高溫  (56度以上半小時) /陽光/酒精殺死<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yo9OgpF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYo9OgpF.jpg&h=153a7964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n顧及口罩過濾層耐熱程度及濕水問題，<br />\n1. 將口罩放入密實袋/潛水套<br />\n2. 熱水池溫度70-90度 (5份滾水+1份水喉水)<br />\n3. 需定時換熱水保持溫度最少30分鐘<br />\n4. 整袋掛起，陽光下再曬2日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wRzeWBr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwRzeWBr.jpg&h=19ed5cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UwoK4SD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUwoK4SD.jpg&h=192e95c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理論上口罩已消毒<br />\n<br />\n處境上，手上已無口罩，亦無渠道購買。<br />\n個人認為<br />\n直接重用口罩 &lt; 不戴口罩 &lt; 重用已消毒口罩 &lt; 不合規格新口罩 &lt; 新口罩 (無法購買)"},{"pid":"4f3cff8e555ee87d0a2d8e76480b8da719c77dbf","tid":1854024,"uid":442,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:44:49.000Z","msg":"隔左層野入面係咪真係有可能56度以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係有辦法56度以上層野會唔會溶<br />\n先唔講病毒死唔死<br />\n但細菌係呢個溫度反而會增強繁殖力<br />\n點解決？"},{"pid":"b9f585b5f5fb7c509dbc209e7485fa9ed4838276","tid":1854024,"uid":229955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:51:00.000Z","msg":"有個user叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>叉燒王子 </strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">開tg group 低價賣口罩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n聲稱有最少10萬個口罩<br />\n全日本最後500個N95係佢手<br />\n係同3M總總部攞貨<br />\n<br />\n要填google from入whatsapp grp俾錢<br />\n<br />\n請各位小心 特別係CD ROM<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n最新消息<br />\n英文名 Ng Wai Chung<br />\n電話 62265933<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6fZZoic.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6fZZoic.png&h=17344ed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有個user叫[size=6][b]叉燒王子 [/b][/size=6]\n[size=4][gold]開tg group 低價賣口罩[/gold][/size=4]\n\n聲稱有最少10萬個口罩\n全日本最後500個N95係佢手\n係同3M總總部攞貨\n\n要填google from入whatsapp grp俾錢\n\n請各位小心 特別係CD ROM\n\n請廣傳\n\n最新消息\n英文名 Ng Wai Chung\n電話 62265933\n[img]https://na.cx/i/6fZZoic.png[/img]</code></pre>"},{"pid":"f2efa3fe2159ddb404f27ceca3571ca1f89cdfc6","tid":1854024,"uid":232065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f3cff8e555ee87d0a2d8e76480b8da719c77dbf","tid":1854024,"uid":442,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:44:49.000Z","msg":"隔左層野入面係咪真係有可能56度以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係有辦法56度以上層野會唔會溶<br />\n先唔講病毒死唔死<br />\n但細菌係呢個溫度反而會增強繁殖力<br />\n點解決？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"個水池夠大，入面應該ok<br />\n但廢老就係廢老，好易做得唔好(e.g. 個袋浮起左，D水凍左，時間唔夠)<br />\n袋入面真係有機會養菌。"},{"pid":"3bf9fa0fd27ecbab83589733d811594a98b895e6","tid":1854024,"uid":235665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"不如煲滾水入密實袋浸"},{"pid":"22f552463601c381bbeb25bd23a95a76e86b1ff9","tid":1854024,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bf9fa0fd27ecbab83589733d811594a98b895e6","tid":1854024,"uid":235665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"不如煲滾水入密實袋浸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:26:30.000Z","msg":"密實袋點頂到滾水﹖"},{"pid":"60390685b8a346f0d3dadcd538993a37e9e47f54","tid":1854024,"uid":9431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020